      <title>布达佩斯旅游区投票禁止 Airbnb 式租赁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/touristic-budapest-district-votes-to-ban-airbnb-style-rentals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于住房成本飙升以及居民对噪音和垃圾的投诉，布达佩斯最具旅游吸引力的地区之一通过全民公投决定禁止短期租赁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/touristic-budapest-district-votes-to-ban-airbnb-style-rentals</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 09:21:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
