    <item>
      <title>南非工作签证改革计划因税收问题而放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/south-african-nomad-visa-slowed-by-tax-issues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非计划通过推出针对远程工作者的“游牧签证”来吸引更多专业人才进入其技术匮乏的经济体，但由于需要修改税收法规，该计划的实施进度受到拖延。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/south-african-nomad-visa-slowed-by-tax-issues</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 06:33:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
